      "content": "<p><span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"the fraction 25 over 4, end fraction, times m, equals, 95\"></span></span></p>\n"
